Secret manager flow
======================= 

AWS secrete manage   ---->  External secrete operator  -----> kubernates secrete ----> pod 

Installation 
==================
Install external secrete operator 


$helm repo add external-secrets https://charts.external-secrets.io

$ helm repo update 

$ helm install external-secrets \
   external-secrets/external-secrets \
    -n external-secrets \
    --create-namespace \
  # --set installCRDs=true

Check weather CRD's are installed ?
$ kubectl get crds | grep secrets


Now apply the manifest files

